<main id="content" class="content"> <header> <h1 class="title">A Prayer of Thanks for Friends</h1>
 <p class="subtitle" role="doc-subtitle">Aug 27, 2016 00:00</p>
</header> <p>
Thank you for the gift of friends, <br></br>
those who are near, <br></br>
and those who are far; <br></br>
those still with us, <br></br>
and those who await us <br></br>
in the life to come.
</p>

 <p>
Kind words remind us <br></br>
that there is no distance, <br></br>
neither time, nor space, <br></br>
neither this life, nor the next, <br></br>
that cannot be crossed.
</p>

 <p>
For nothing can separate us <br></br>
from the love of God, <br></br>
and by that same love, <br></br>
we are connected to each other.
</p>

 <p>
 <i>Amen</i>
</p>


